title: GEORGE BURNS and GRACIE ALLEN SHOW ( -- filmed in color )
description:
I uploaded this 5th Season opener before, but that was a black & white print.
CBS was doing experimental color broadcasts of a lot of their TV series in 19554,
including several episodes of The Red Skelton Show, The Jackie Gleason Show
and this Burns and Allen Show episode!  The color effect was a little faded,
at least with this, the only surviving film print of any of the CBS shows.

Gracie Allen was said to be nervous about being on color film, because she
supposedly had to have different color eyeballs. I think that's hard to tell!
